{"tid":1777074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊睇下藍絲係幾自私","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T04:08:09.000Z","uid":244417,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12394e3657a2188db0511680e798911ba2b0eb1b","tid":1777074,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebe00b505612ac70aa5366f56bfa1653c40a6ce","tid":1777074,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cd69a66edb76c9378e97a9265ccc181a7d30929","tid":1777074,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5a6516666e818969190823083bec2b31778e312","tid":1777074,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"仲有7個鐘就係啦... 跪求大家入嚟睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy3vV3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy3vV3M.jpg&h=7e318a13&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要今晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際人權日．正日集會】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過7個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"489bf312071330719375e236d2bc28e60580857d","tid":1777074,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"984fcd6eef13fa77fe0a0167177d83804f0037f1","tid":1777074,"uid":213163,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQGEPDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQGEPDi.jpg&h=fa3b95a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0597a1691443049e8ccb9ad27c338e18118e2d2","tid":1777074,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"好撚假<br />\n又話唔介意用呢2 個字<br />\n但又話「你呢兩個字」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實「硬要撐藍店」個思路係咪唔想為啖氣咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52cc37b677b8947d4dc3803ad064b6ae4e8a676","tid":1777074,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20427f76d5551c62e4a1c8d2d3ff7eed58c872f9","tid":1777074,"uid":244417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b404c70344bcdcc683c42b23b503e383749d2c7","tid":1777074,"uid":244417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"984fcd6eef13fa77fe0a0167177d83804f0037f1","tid":1777074,"uid":213163,"like":5,"dislike":0,